Before starting the test suite make sure the environment is setup with the following
 1. Close all applications other than Ranorex (including PLMWorx, SolidWorks, and Skype for Business) 
 2. Install the SolidWorks add-in for the current environment 
 3. Run CopyLoginInfo.bat
 4. Edit C:\home\PLM_Deploy_Test\cell6\login.xlsb and update the username and passwords
 5. Adjust the global parameters
   a. For QA use: 
  	    LaunchBatchFile				\\ca01a9001\pgmis\Development\ATSPLM PLM Test Files\Environment Launchers\QA.bat

	b. for DEV use:
  	    LaunchBatchFile				\\ca01a9001\pgmis\Development\ATSPLM PLM Test Files\Environment Launchers\DEV.bat